	(text "3v3 supply using LDO tested on other boards. \nExpected current draw is max ~200ma.\n\n5V supply taken from CM4 I/O breakout board.\n\nIdeally, a PMOS with higher Vgs than DMG2307 \nwould be better. (Vgs for DMG2307 is rated at \n+/- 30V which could be OK). Doing so would \nprovide more headroom above the Dz Voltage\nprotection vs. Vmax for the FETS"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 112.522 190.246 0)
		(effects
